Etaaraki enkaji e Saul metuata


1  Netii apa olameyu too nkolong'i e Daudi too larin okuni, to lari ake o to lari, neing'oru Daudi enkomom o Laitoriani. Nejo Olaitoriani, “Etii entorroni o sarge shumata Saul o shumata enkaji enye, enkaraki natara Ilgibioni metuata.” 
2   Neaku eipoto olaiguanani Ilgibioni. Ore apa Ilgibioni neme iloo ltung'ana le Israel, kake ilo lpisiai loo Lamori; hoo neinosa iltung'ana le Israel olmumai pee eleku ninche, etonyuaa Saul ear ninche metuata te ina nyuata enye te nkaraki iltung'ana le Israel o Yuda. 
3  Nejoki Daudi lelo Gibioni, “Kaa nanu aitaas intae? Naa kaji nanu aikunu enkipooto, pee itumutumu intae aatamayian enjung'ore o Laitoriani?” 
4  Nejoki ilgibioni ninye, “Mme mbae e nkosholai arashu sahabu erishata ang o Saul arashu enkaji enye; neme enaang pee kiar oltung'ani metua te Israel.” Nejo ninye, “Ijojo intae pee aitaas aa nanu intae?” 
5  Nejoki ninche olaiguanani, “Ore ilo tung'ani apa otumuta iyiook neitobir pee eidaikie iyiook, metaa mikitum iyiook ewueji ti atua enkop pooki oo Siraeli. 
6  Nchoo meishori ilayiok lenyena oopishana pee kisiong iyiook ninche te dukuya Olaitoriani te Gibeon to ldoinyo lo Laitoriani.” Nejo olaiguanani, “Kaishoru nanu ninche.”


7   Kake etelekua olaiguanani Mefiboshet, olayioni lo layioni le Saul, Yonatan, te nkaraki olmumai lo Laitoriani apa otii erishata ninche, o erishata e Daudi, o Yonatan olayioni le Saul. 
8   Neya olaiguanani ilayiok oare le Rispa entito e Aia apa naa ninye etoikio Saul, Armon o Mefiboshet; o layiok imiet le Merab entito e Saul laa ninche etoikio Adriel olayioni le Barsilai ilo Meholati; 
9  neishooyo ninche apik atua nkaik oo Lgibioni; neilili ninche teilo doinyo te dukuya Olaitoriani, ore ninche pokira oopishana neidak te nebo. Neari ninche metuata too nkolong'i e dukuya e nkisampuare, te nkiterunoto e nkisampuare e shairi.


10  Neitoki Rispa entito e Aia aya ilkuniyiani neisalaashaki te ndapidapoi ebaiki enkiterunoto e nkisampuare o metaba anaa neshaiki enchan ninche eing'uaa shumata; neitu ninye eisho imotonyi o loing'ang'e epuonu aadoiki ninche te ndama, arashu ing'uesi e ong'ata te nkewarie. 
11  Ore ake pee elikini Daudi enataasa Rispa entito e Aia ina apiani e Saul, 
12   nelo Daudi aitayu iloik le Saul o loik lo layioni lenye Yonatan ti atua iltung'ana le Yabesh-gilead, apa ootupurroitie ninche to lkurroto otumoreki te Bet-shan, te ine apa neililiyie Ilfilisti ninche, te ina olong apa nataara Ilfilisti Saul metua te Gilboa; 
13  neyau ninye ailepunye te ine iloik le Saul o loik lo layioni lenye Yonatan; neiturrur ninche iloik le lelo apa oo lilioki. 
14  Nenukaa ninche iloik le Saul o layioni lenye Yonatan te nkop e Benchamen te Sela, ti atua enkurare e Kish papaai lenye; neas ninche nena pooki naaitanapishe olaiguanani. Ore te siadi ina nening Enkai eomonokinoto te nkaraki enkop.

