15  Nenyaakitia apa Ilfilisti aata olarrabal o Israel, nedoyio Daudi alo te nebo isinkan lenyena nearare ninche Ilfilisti; neilepunye Daudi. 
16  Ore Ishbi-benob, obo apa le ishoi e lelo tung'ana sapuki laa shekeli iip o suyai enkirroishi e mpere enye, oenita olalem ng'ejuk, neing'oru pee ear Daudi metua. 
17   Kake eewuo Abishai olayioni le Seruiya aretu, nerasaki ilo Filisti near ninye metua. Neitirrishaki iltung'ana le Daudi ninye aajoki, “Mintoki aekata iyie aipang alo te nebo iyiook olarrabal, pee miar ake olkilang'ilang'et le Israel.”


18  Ore te siadi ena neitoki atii olarrabal apa o Lfilisti te Gob; neari metua Sibekai ol Husati Saf, laa ninye apa obo le ishoi e lelo tung'ana sapuki. 
19  Neetae ake sii apa olarrabal o Lfilisti te Gob; neari Elhanan olayioni le Yaareoregim, le Betlehem near metua Goliat le Giti oba enchata e mpere enye anaa embokishi o lashetani. 
20  Neetae sii apa olarrabal te Gas, teine apa netii oltung'ani sapuk oado oata lkimojik ile te pooki aina, o nkimojik ile te pooki keju, tikitam o ong'uan esiana e pooki; naa ole ishoi sii apa ninye e lelo tung'ana sapuki. 
21  Ore ake pee edek ninye Israel near ninye metua Yonatan olayioni le Shimei, ilo alashe le Daudi. 
22  Ore kulo oong'uan naa ile ishoi e lelo tung'ana apa sapuki ootii Gas; near Daudi te nkaina enye o te nkaina oo sinkan lenyena metuata.

